Daruruwan mutane sun taru a daya daga cikin rairayin bakin teku na birnin Paulo a ranar Juma'a don halartar bikin, lokacin da raƙuman ruwa mai tsawon mita shida (18 ft) ya buge rairayin bakin teku kuma ya ɗauki gawawwakin mutane tare da shi yana lalata duk abin da ya zo a hanyarsa.
Tsunami ya biyo bayan girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.5.
Wani wakilin kamfanin BNPB, wanda ke kula da annobar Indonesiya ta Sutofo Purwo Nugrohon`, a wani taron manema labarai a Jakarta, ya bayyana cewa, jiya, lokacin da tashin hankali game da tsunami ya tashi, mutane sun ci gaba da aikinsu a bakin rairayin bakin teku kuma maimakon haka sun gudu daga wurin, wanda ya sa suka zama wadanda suka rasa rayukansu.
"Tsunami bai zo da kansa ba, ya kawo motoci, fursunoni, gidaje, ya buge komai a ƙasa", in ji Nugrohoon, yana ƙara da cewa kafin ya haɗu da rairayin bakin teku, tsunami ya yi tafiya a teku mai saurin 800 km/h.
